title: THE 24-HOUR RULE OF BRAGGING: Why It's Essential To Your Success, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO301
itunes:title: THE 24-HOUR RULE OF BRAGGING: Why It's Essential To Your Success, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO301
description: If you could take a time machine back to your biggest win in life…would you? If you’re thinking “Of course! I'd love to rocket back to Yesteryear to relive the Glory Days," then your chances of being a real success in life are probable zero. ZERO. Truly successful people have a completely different mindset. They are guided by a major rule in life: The 24-Hour Rule of Bragging. This rule protects you from mediocrity and helps you move on from massive mistakes.
